title: Missions for Thief 2: The Metal Age (rel. 2017-12-28)
description:
658 Missions for Thief 2: The Metal Age

game version 1.18 required
patch NewDark v1.25 required

every archive contains FM.INI for FM Selector

.stuff/FMINI_Only.7z - standalone fm.ini
.stuff/libmp3lame.7z - required dll (put it with thief2.exe)
.stuff/MissionList.7z - HTML-list of missions with descriptions and preview links
.stuff/Ricebug's_Walkthroughs.7z - Walkthroughs for some missions
.stuff/t2scripts.7z - actual scripts
.stuff/ChangeLog.7z - small history
.stuff/checksum.7z - md5 checksums
